017-09-15T11:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/DxAIA26amNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDxAIA26amNo&d=93cIGimYQZdYcVrfrhOtITOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1eb06879\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DxAIA26amNo</a><br />\n一定係呢場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好正常</blockquote><br />\n失個啲波既錯誤都好低級wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992bd29374d8346828cc5e1a80a759aa109aeccd","tid":400232,"uid":30804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西甲既拉斯澎馬斯<br />\n意甲全部球隊<br />\n法甲里昂<br />\n日職日乙韓職中超墨超都好撚假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比較正常反而係美職</blockquote><br />\n上星期a米冇啦啦十分鐘輸四球係未假波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得德甲拜仁都好假咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成日贏波輸盤／最尾先入波／反cup殺半主，主主咁 超哂班睇住黎食 隨時㩒製就入波咁 見佢幾次補時先絕殺 落後都可以反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1b50b6e4ddc2a91dc34b8172315b9315ee15ae","tid":400232,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"認真講<br />\n如果有踢開波既話<br />\n就會明要做假真係好易<br />\nmark人企開少少 落地落慢少少 射波射比龍 12碼射上月球  <br />\n難睇d既有 進攻防守陣式好散<br />\n<br />\n例子 岩岩8強 恆大對上海 <br />\n都做得好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6b263a5e405852ca8f6f69fc0b733abab752ba","tid":400232,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:09:42.000Z","msg":"發覺呢啲片YouTube bam得好快,個聯賽以版權理由要消失"}]}